Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.toptica.TopMode, [
    "(param-ref 'laser1:wavelength)", "(param-ref 'laser2:wavelength)"], [
    "(param-ref 'laser1:wavelength)", '640',
    "> (param-ref 'laser2:wavelength)", '405.3', '> '], sep='\r\n') as tm:
    assert tm.laser[0].wavelength == 640 * u.nm
    assert tm.laser[1].wavelength == 405.3 * u.nm
